(Hahaha! Atma as second in command. Good one! As I recall JP said 
Quickstrike was going to be second in command.)


Quickstrike:





Quickstrike made his way down to a corridor where there were multible doors 
that lead to the quarters. As he recalled there were at least two corridors 
with quarters. Not all rooms where quarters as he found out. He didn't want 
to have her too close to his quarters.

He kept walking down. He decided a quarters for Dark Mouse would be all 
right, but not so close to his. She may just tag along too much, but he 
could help her out since she wasn't at her best.

He checked a door at the right side of the corridor. It was unlocked so he 
pressed a botton on the side that made the door slide open. He was just in 
luck. It was an empty quarters and it had good enough room for Dark Mouse. 
These sets of quarters that the Trypicon had were huge compared to the 
Darkside's, and he liked it. He looked around it fully and nodded in 
approval. He walked out and closed it behind him. He walked back to the lab 
room where Dark Mouse and Black Arachnia were. He leaned against the frame 
of the door and waited for Black Arachnia to finish with Dark Mouse.
